high_descs: Go to the counter left of the sink
Pick up a dirty bowl from the counter
Wash the bowl in the sink
Place the bowl on a shelf
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned bowl on a shelf

high_descs: Turn to the right, and left to find the stove.
Pick up the bowl from behind the wine bottle.
Hold the bowl and take a few steps left to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the bowl.
Carry the bowl of water and turn around. Go across to the shelf on the right side.
Place the bowl on the next to bottom shelf, on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Clean a bowl and fill it with water. Place it on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right then walk straight and head to the counter
Pick up the bowl on the counter in between the stove and sink
Turn right make a step face the sink
Put the bowl in the sink and fill in water
Turn left walk straight cross the room head to the shelf rack
Put the bowl with water on the shelf rack
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with water on the shelf rack
